    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. Austrophthiracarus cronadun sp. nov.: 1, lateral view of body (legs removed); 2, prodorsum, dorsal view; 3, left side of genito-aggenital plate; 4, left side of anoadanal plate; 5, subcapitulum, palpi removed; 6, palp, antiaxial view; 7, chelicera, antiaxial view; 8, femur I; 9, tibia IV. Scale bars: 1, 2, 3, 4, 8, 9=100 µm; 5, 6, 7=50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098505/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

